As the time nears for the 2019 elections, the political season gets more intense. The APC gathered in Osogbo on 18 September to support one of their own, Adegboyega Oyetola Oyetola campaigning for governor of Osun State. President Muhammadu Buhari with other APC chieftains was present. While some people are grumbling about the state of Osun state and are questioning why they should even bother to vote for the party, others are pledging their undying loyalty. Some Nigerians aired their views via Twitter.       